title: Second Chancellor Candidate, Joseph E. Steinmetz, to Hold Public Forum (University of Arkansas)
text: ( Source : University of Arkansas ) Photo Submitted Joseph Steinmetz. FAYETTEVILLE, Ark. - Joseph E. Steinmetz, the second of three candidates for the position of University of Arkansas chancellor, will hold an open public forum at 10:30 a.m.
